{"tid":1498091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人可以容許我行得更前，然後離開","createTime":"2019-08-23T08:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T13:04:46.000Z","uid":175567,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e203b8a3d376fc9df459915c7ae426b4cf24c0d6","tid":1498091,"uid":175567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:58:08.000Z","msg":"多謝你入黎聽我講廢話先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟我經歷左69 100萬大遊行，612添華道，616 200萬+1大遊行，621 包圍狗總，630煲底，71朝早夏慤道中路，夜晚立法會，714 沙田，721 上環 ，727元朗，81 馬鞍山，84 將軍澳 上環 銅鑼灣，85 黃大仙，811 尖沙嘴 818 和平遊行。唔係去曬所有反送中事件講聲唔好意思先。<br />\n<br />\n係818之前，我只係一個所謂嘅普通前線，612添華差D被包抄，630煲底同撐警人對罵，71阻止升旗，夜晚入立法會，721差D中催淚彈碎片等等。我知有好多人嘅經歷恐怖過我，所以我冇資格話其他人唔夠前，唔夠勇。<br />\n<br />\n但係呢D經歷我唔可以詳細同老豆老母、同學、朋友講，只可以輕輕帶過，因為怕佢地擔心或者覺得我係到曬命。所以每次自己一個行動嘅經歷、畫面都甚少分享，而我係呢兩個星期開始頂唔到，開始想去死。但係我唔可以自殺，因為家人、朋友會傷心。<br />\n<br />\n所以我想行得更前，被狗開槍打死，至少比我人生最後一刻都係有用，就係激起香港人嘅憤怒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思我講得1999，但呢D壓力已經越來越大，好難頂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358c5507a40ef9aca8a13cabbb6bbed15b63f482","tid":1498091,"uid":84104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:00:54.000Z","msg":"佢哋係唔會開槍打死你<br />\n只會衝埋嚟打鳩你拘捕你再虐待你"},{"pid":"f1eabd13bd1be68597d4ef958f17e2ced624ed52","tid":1498091,"uid":101498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:03:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">是日（823星期五）活動<br />\n銀髮族罷買<br />\n會計界遊行<br />\n基督徒集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">人鏈</span><br />\n賣港城一日遊</div></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BXTv9tG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBXTv9tG.png&h=e866629a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">光復香港，時代革命</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e356f678af2d2b7d365cf56e6086fb50a39046b2","tid":1498091,"uid":175567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"358c5507a40ef9aca8a13cabbb6bbed15b63f482","tid":1498091,"uid":84104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:00:54.000Z","msg":"佢哋係唔會開槍打死你<br />\n只會衝埋嚟打鳩你拘捕你再虐待你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:08:49.000Z","msg":"錦我到時只希望可以打死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16822a0d23cb20b575b62b32757e2331ceb6e55","tid":1498091,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:41:55.000Z","msg":"same"},{"pid":"ee48747fb52230c14638eff64141a1fe4a27d99a","tid":1498091,"uid":175567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c16822a0d23cb20b575b62b32757e2331ceb6e55","tid":1498091,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:41:55.000Z","msg":"same"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}